Package: review
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Robson Ricardo <your-email@example.com>
Installed-Size: 40
Depends: python3-gi, python3:any, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, gir1.2-glib-2.0
Section: education
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/jobsr/Review
Description: Spaced Repetition Study Manager
 Review is a modern GNOME application for managing your study schedule
 using the spaced repetition technique. It helps you remember what you
 learn by scheduling reviews at optimal intervals.
 .
 Features:
  - Automatic scheduling using spaced repetition (7, 15, 30 days)
  - Built-in study timer with session tracking
  - Calendar views (monthly and weekly)
  - Topic organization by areas and tags
  - Study time statistics
  - Beautiful GNOME/Libadwaita interface
